  "description": "A panoramic view of a bay area landscape partially obscured by dense fog or mist. A long bridge stretches across the water, receding into the distance. In the background, rolling hills and the outlines of a city skyline are faintly visible through the fog, creating a layered effect. A small vessel is visible on the water. The light filters through the fog, creating dramatic shafts of light that illuminate patches of water and land. The overall impression is one of atmospheric perspective and ethereal beauty.",
